Tandon Corp said it hasagreed in principle to sell to personal computer maker &lt;AmstradPLC> during 1987 about 50 mln dlrs of 20 megabyte Winchesterdisk drives.    It said shipments have already begun and about 30 mln dlrsof the drives are scheduled for delivery during the first half. The drives are in half-height configuration. Reuter&#3;